name: spywhere's Projects
body:
### Welcome to my GitHub pages.
These are my projects on GitHub. Most of them are from [Bukkit.org](http://bukkit.org)
Feels free to folk it :)

* [SimpleIn1](https://github.com/spywhere/SimpleIn1) - My first CraftBukkit plugin
* [AdvLog](https://github.com/spywhere/AdvLog) - An advanced logging plugin (for CraftBukkit)
* [DebuggerSample](https://github.com/spywhere/DebuggerSample) - Sample project for Debugger (CraftBukkit plugin)
* [MFSSample](https://github.com/spywhere/MFSSample) - Sample project for MFS (CraftBukkit plugin)
* [MFSExtendSample](https://github.com/spywhere/MFSExtendSample) - Sample project for MFSExtend (Spoutcraft plugin)
* [S2S](https://github.com/spywhere/S2S) - Multi-server connection plugin (for CraftBukkit)


### Contact Me

https://github.com/spywhere
